ygData.messageBody:
just follow the shore line at the first stop and you see the man and then up
to the left you'll see a stone and that is where the woman is, they aren't
linked either. They can hit up to 100 pts per round (50 per punch), maybe
more if kick would max out too. Usually they only hit you for 50 max
though. If your on povar they are mine for a while :)

Barry

Vanelin 29th level nec
